#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:221
msgid "Prerelease bump rules:"
msgstr "Reglas de incremento prerelease:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:223
msgid ""
"Bumping a stable version to `alpha`, `beta`, or `rc` first increments the "
"patch version, then enters the target channel starting from `.1`."
msgstr ""
"Al incrementar una versiﾃｳn estable a `alpha`, `beta` o `rc`, primero se "
"incrementa la versiﾃｳn patch y luego se entra en el canal objetivo desde `.1`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:225
msgid ""
"`prepatch`, `preminor`, and `premajor` start a fresh prerelease from the "
"next patch, minor, or major version respectively, such as `1.2.3 -> "
"1.3.0-rc.1` with `preminor` + `rc`."
msgstr ""
"`prepatch`, `preminor` y `premajor` inician una nueva prerelease desde la "
"siguiente versiﾃｳn patch, minor o major respectivamente, por ejemplo `1.2.3 -"
"> 1.3.0-rc.1` con `preminor` + `rc`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:228
msgid ""
"Bumping within the same channel increments the sequence number, such as `"
"alpha.1 -> alpha.2`."
msgstr ""
"Al incrementar dentro del mismo canal se aumenta el nﾃｺmero de secuencia, "
"como `alpha.1 -> alpha.2`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:230
msgid ""
"`release` removes prerelease and build metadata while keeping the same "
"`major.minor.patch` values, such as `1.2.3-rc.2 -> 1.2.3`."
msgstr ""
"`release` elimina los metadatos de prerelease y build manteniendo el mismo "
"`major.minor.patch`, por ejemplo `1.2.3-rc.2 -> 1.2.3`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:232
msgid ""
"Channel promotion is allowed (`alpha -> beta -> rc`), but channel downgrade "
"is not (for example, `rc -> beta` raises an error)."
msgstr ""
"Se permite promocionar de canal (`alpha -> beta -> rc`), pero no degradarlo "
"por ejemplo `rc -> beta` produce un error."

